data.description: * Improved Price - Bring all offers * This incredible home offers just the right amount of space and flow for your family. On the first level you have a great room out front for dinning or office space, One full Bath, and One bedroom with walk-in closet. Kitchen has an open concept feel attached to the spacious family room, which is a great space to entertain and  keep everyone together. Granite counter tops and Plantation Shutters in the family room. On the second level, you will find a lovely loft area, laundry room and three additional bedrooms, the master suite being one of the three very spacious bedrooms, complete with separate tub and shower, generously sized walk-in closet.  Unfinished basement allows for your own custom creation to expand however you would like.
